Rusty vs. the Robo Squirrel / Rusty's Day of the Drones When the robotic squirrel Rusty made goes rogue - swiping things from all over town, Rusty and Ruby must find a way to capture Robo-Squirrel and his loot.
Frankie Fritz uses a handful of homemade drones to swipe Rusty and Ruby's Mega Battery (2018)!
